{"tid":1583754,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"連登又畀人帶風向，返返去之前嘅情況","createTime":"2019-09-20T18:35:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T05:04:59.000Z","uid":80936,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"78b51de25e9e8e0c7008d45c5c5326143e7dcceb","tid":1583754,"uid":80936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T18:35:13.000Z","msg":"而家有白色箱嘅圖出現<br />\n開始將之前將軍澳白色箱單嘢嘅線索連埋一齊<br />\n然後又有人彈出嚟話要fact check咗先信<br />\n<br />\n喂，之前唔係講好咗<br />\n話要拎證據出嚟澄清謠言嘅係班狗<br />\n我哋唔需要幫佢哋fact check咩？<br />\n<br />\n做文宣嘅材料<br />\n係真係要fact check咗先可以信<br />\n<br />\n但唔代表未fact check嘅嘢<br />\n我哋自己人唔信得㗎嘛<br />\n<br />\n而家班狗搵人帶風向<br />\n叫你哋唔好信<br />\n你哋就真係唔信？<br />\n<br />\n而且呢單嘢又咁驚炒車做乜嘢<br />\n炒咗車對我哋嚟講<br />\n係好事喎<br />\n話曬都證實咗係冇人死喎<br />\n<br />\n而且我哋有呢個懷疑都好正常啫<br />\n人命關天喎<br />\n<br />\n你哋唔覺呢單嘢好奇怪咩？<br />\n又係好似新屋嶺咁<br />\n有班人出嚟帶風向<br />\n話未fact check唔好信呢單<br />\n<br />\n但又係冇人講話唔好信831單嘢<br />\n<br />\n同樣兩單案都係有懷點<br />\n一個就係三個人消失<br />\n一個就係有白色箱出現<br />\n<br />\n我同你哋講<br />\n班狗一定會企出嚟話<br />\n個白色箱係用嚟裝死者屍體<br />\n因為喺岸邊發現咗屍體<br />\n所以先至要拎個白色箱裝<br />\n<br />\n但你哋諗下<br />\n點解無啦啦會係咁偏僻嘅位發現屍體<br />\n如果班狗話個箱係用嚟裝屍體<br />\n未即係話將軍澳差館個白色箱<br />\n都係用嚟裝屍體㗎囉<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">未fact check係唔可以做文宣<br />\n但係唔代表我地唔信得</span></strong><br />\n醒下啦香港人<br />\n<br />\n政府夠話智能燈柱上面個發射器同大陸冇關係啦<br />\n但係你哋又唔信？<br />\n你哋fact check咗真係送去大陸啦咩？<br />\n<br />\n政府大把手段可以令你知件事<br />\n但你唔會 fact check到<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>因為可以用來做白色恐怖呀嘛</strong></span>"},{"pid":"9d2dbbc8cd6f2fc24f35274c6af9c2eb00a09684","tid":1583754,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T18:35:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">由於都係有好多人唔明行動有咩意義同目標 於是係正式攻略之前出個簡化版</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【行動】【主線】 【922】【SUCK4.0】 【多圖】 【簡易式攻略目標 】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1583476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1583476</a>"},{"pid":"4b39dd2f5c4c364cc65853d7eaa1e453101aed0f","tid":1583754,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T18:39:40.000Z","msg":"注意力有限<br />\n唔好不斷捕風捉影"},{"pid":"af5bb3e97c5b9b2d07f2ee539eb71bb7564407f7","tid":1583754,"uid":211034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T05:04:59.000Z","msg":"一齊去Twitter將 #929globalantichinazimarch <br />\n推上熱門 <br />\n推到929全世界所有人都一齊standwithHK<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mjKZ7PA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmjKZ7PA.jpg&h=9c9f7bc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5sn1BHW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5sn1BHW.jpg&h=f59429dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/stjbYWh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FstjbYWh.jpg&h=231ca5f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QW0OgHY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQW0OgHY.jpg&h=d6c222cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/opCg92Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FopCg92Z.jpg&h=5bd6bb90&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}